  "title": "Operations Manager",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><p>Oversee daily construction operations and site activities</p><p>Plan, coordinate, and monitor project schedules, manpower, and resources</p><p>Ensure works comply with BCA regulations, safety standards, and quality requirements</p><p>Liaise with clients, consultants, subcontractors, and suppliers</p><p>Control project costs, progress, and timely completion</p><p>Handle site issues, reporting, and operational improvements</p><p></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>Degree in Engineering or related field</p><p>Minimum 2–6 years’ experience in construction operations </p><p>Strong knowledge of local regulations, safety, and site management</p><p>Good leadership, coordination, and problem-solving skills</p><p>Able to manage multiple projects independently</p>",
